_______________________________________________________________________________
"Project Thought" 
        This is basically an 'area tell'.  It projects a thought not
        to a specific target, but to an entire room full of people.
        Combined with clairaudience, it allows the psionicist to have
        conversations from afar with groups of people while he or she
        is at an entirely different location of Darkwind.  
 
SP Cost:  5		Guild Level:  1		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  project <target> <message>
